data.description: Beautiful, turn-key home with an upgraded kitchen, flooring, and paint. The home offers 3 bedrooms with large restrooms in the master and guest baths. The home is equipped with Solar Power that is leased and can get transferred to the buyer at closing. The monthly power bill averages about $30 dollars. The backyard is spacious and the community offers a pool for all of your entertaining needs!
